titles.title: Electing officers of the House of Representatives.

action.text: On agreeing to the first portion of the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.
On agreeing to the remainder of the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by voice vote.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 1/5/2011--Passed House without amendment. Elects the following officers of the House of Representatives: (1) Karen L. Haas as Clerk; (2) Wilson S. Livingood as Sergeant at Arms; (3) Daniel J. Strodel as Chief Administrative Officer; and (4) Father Daniel P. Coughlin as Chaplain.
